{"tid":504312,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"知唔知零食物語個名點黎？","createTime":"2017-12-19T21:42:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-19T22:30:09.000Z","uid":64131,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"418d371499cc77d8cd545af877c15b9abdf732c5","tid":504312,"uid":64131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T21:42:17.000Z","msg":"零食物語，其實解「寧食勿語」<br />\n<br />\n後生果陣<br />\n見到唔合理既事，就會好勇敢咁樣出黎同人理論<br />\n就算全世界都反對你所相信既野<br />\n你都會覺得事情係有絕對既對錯<br />\n只要堅持己見<br />\n星星之火  可以爎原<br />\n總有日個世界會企喺你果邊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到大個<br />\n發現其實好多事冇絕對既對錯<br />\n可能你做左好多野   原來都係徒勞無功<br />\n因為其他人根本冇興趣去理<br />\n只係想過好自己既生活<br />\n漸漸地  你都唔想同人拗咁多<br />\n寧願留番啖氣   食飽個肚就算<br />\n<br />\n呢個就係「零食物語」既典故"},{"pid":"e401eb4426f8c6c7fdec03eebcb44e09662013fc","tid":504312,"uid":2313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T21:44:34.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"a440e4b32c45050b19e20ab3df27439536243dd5","tid":504312,"uid":152437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T22:18:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4c8c165f3b95e933ae7b7fa195f82e4b5e730f22","tid":504312,"uid":152437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T22:18:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0af5d98126499c0b390c55fa8f57dc08ed81b033","tid":504312,"uid":152437,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T22:18:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"168fa5ce5b4911339c2b15b7be1c8b25cd371dea","tid":504312,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T22:30:09.000Z","msg":"下？"}]}